# SEO — Suspiros de Papel

Phase 1 launch checklist items. Priority order: Crawlability → Technical → On-Page → Content.

## Meta Tags (app/layout.tsx)

```tsx
export const metadata: Metadata = {
  title: {
    template: "%s | Suspiros de Papel",
    default: "Suspiros de Papel — Regalos personalizados en Zihuatanejo",
  },
  description: "Sublimación, grabado láser y papelería personalizada en Zihuatanejo, Guerrero. Pide tu cotización por WhatsApp.",
  keywords: ["regalos personalizados", "sublimación Zihuatanejo", "grabado láser Guerrero"],
  openGraph: {
    type: "website",
    locale: "es_MX",
    url: "https://suspirosdepapel.mx",
    siteName: "Suspiros de Papel",
  },
  twitter: { card: "summary_large_image" },
  robots: { index: true, follow: true },
}
```

## robots.txt (public/robots.txt)

```
User-agent: *
Allow: /
Sitemap: https://suspirosdepapel.mx/sitemap.xml
```

## sitemap.xml (app/sitemap.ts)

```ts
import { MetadataRoute } from "next"

export default function sitemap(): MetadataRoute.Sitemap {
  return [
    { url: "https://suspirosdepapel.mx", lastModified: new Date(), changeFrequency: "monthly", priority: 1 },
    { url: "https://suspirosdepapel.mx/portafolio", lastModified: new Date(), changeFrequency: "weekly", priority: 0.8 },
  ]
}
```

## JSON-LD Schema (app/layout.tsx or page.tsx)

```tsx
const schema = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "LocalBusiness",
  name: "Suspiros de Papel",
  description: "Regalos personalizados en Zihuatanejo",
  address: { "@type": "PostalAddress", addressLocality: "Zihuatanejo", addressRegion: "Guerrero", addressCountry: "MX" },
  telephone: SITE.whatsapp,
  url: "https://suspirosdepapel.mx",
}

<script type="application/ld+json" dangerouslySetInnerHTML={{ __html: JSON.stringify(schema) }} />
```

## Core Web Vitals Targets

- LCP < 2.5s → use `priority` on hero image, `next/image` for all portfolio
- CLS < 0.1 → explicit width/height on all images, no layout shifts
- INP < 200ms → no heavy client-side JS in Phase 1

## Image SEO

- All images: descriptive Spanish `alt` text
- Portfolio images: `.webp` format, explicit dimensions
- OG image: 1200×630px at `public/og-image.jpg`

## Audit Before Launch

Run `/seo-audit` in Claude Code for full pre-launch check.
Priority: technical SEO → on-page → content → performance.
